text: Bumetopia bakeri is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1927 and is known from the Philippines.BioLib.cz - Bumetopia bakeri. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1927
title: Bumetopia bakeri
